OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1777227067
OL,3,CRow over Bobby Sands Belfast statue
OL,5,FA political row has erupted after
OL,6,FBelfast city councillors voted to
OL,7,Freconsider a decision allowing statue
OL,8,Fof IRA hunger striker Bobby Sands to
OL,9,Fremain in place, despite not having
OL,10,Fplanning permission.
OL,12,FThe Bobby Sands Trust accused
OL,13,Funionists of "hypocrisy" following the
OL,14,Fvote on Thursday night.
OL,16,FThe statue was unveiled at the
OL,17,FRepublican Memorial Garden in
OL,18,FTwinbrook, west Belfast, last year to
OL,19,Fmark the 44th anniversary of the
OL,20,Fformer MP's death.
OL,26,@uD@NOUuD@XO]
