PN,44702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1777227067
OL,3,CRow over Bobby Sands Belfast statue
OL,5,FBelfast City Council confirmed that
OL,6,Fwhile no planning application was ever
OL,7,Fsubmitted, they had not previously
OL,8,Ftaken any action.
OL,10,FAt the meeting on Thursday, a DUP
OL,11,Fmotion was passed calling for the
OL,12,Fmatter to be reconsidered.
OL,14,FA Sinn Fein amendment seeking a review
OL,15,Fof the "current enforcement status of
OL,16,Fall such structures" across the
OL,17,Fcouncil area was unsuccessful.
OL,26,@vD@IrrwD@HOUxD@TO]
