OL,3,CRow over Bobby Sands Belfast statue
OL,5,FBobby Sands at the age of 27, died on
OL,6,FMay 5, 1981. He was the first of 10
OL,7,Fparamilitary prisoners to die during
OL,8,Fthe Maze prison hunger strike.
OL,10,FThe father-of-one had been elected an
OL,11,FMP for Fermanagh and South Tyrone less
OL,12,Fthan a month before his death.
OL,14,FDanny Morrison, secretary of the Bobby
OL,15,FSands Trust and a former director of
OL,16,Fpublicity for Sinn Fein, criticised
OL,17,Fthe SDLP for abstaining during the
OL,18,Fvote.
OL,26,@xD@Urr
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
