FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1777227067
OL,3,CRow over Bobby Sands Belfast statue
OL,5,FIn statement, he said: "There is no
OL,6,Fcost to the ratepayers of Belfast for
OL,7,Fthis statue, a statue supported by
OL,8,Flocal people who came out in their
OL,9,Fthousands for its unveiling.
OL,11,F"We know the real reason for this
OL,12,Fdebate has got nothing to do with a
OL,13,Funiversal principle to be applied to
OL,14,Feveryone but everything to do with
OL,15,Funionists resenting the fact they can
OL,16,Fno longer control the narrative about
OL,17,Fthe history of Belfast and how there
OL,18,Fare no longer second-class citizens in
OL,19,Fthis city.
OL,21,F"The hypocrisy is astonishing.
OL,26,@mD@XOUsD@AOU}D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
