OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1777227067
OL,3,CRow over Bobby Sands Belfast statue
OL,5,FHe said: "Memorials and sites of
OL,6,Fremembrance across Belfast hold deep
OL,7,Femotional and historical significance.
OL,9,F"Approaches to enforcement must
OL,10,Ftherefore be proportionate, sensitive,
OL,11,Fand rooted in respect.
OL,13,F"Priority should be given to
OL,14,Fengagement, dialogue, and community-
OL,15,Fled solutions, particularly where
OL,16,Fstructures serve a commemorative
OL,17,Fpurpose and pose no safety risk."
OL,26,@mD@JOUqD@AOUuD@AOUyD@aO]
