OL,3,CRow over Bobby Sands Belfast statue
OL,5,FFirst Minister Michelle O'Neill and
OL,6,Fformer Sinn Fein president Gerry Adams
OL,7,Fwere among those who attended the
OL,8,Funveiling of the statue last year.
OL,10,FMs O'Neill had called it "a powerful
OL,11,Ftribute".
